reviews.review_text: A good spot featuring healthy and tasty bowls. At first the portion sizing seemed small but I enjoyed a regular sized porketta bowl with a coffee and it was filling for the entire day. Prices were also reasonable and the food was prepared fresh by the friendly owners.

Newly opened vegan, GF friendly restaurant with option of building your own bowl. The menu is really simple and clean. Large food portion and tastes delicious!! The staff is really friendly and the environment is super clean. If you live near by KITS definitely come by trying them out. Will be back soon! Keep it up Gobble
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you Tario! Were happy that you liked our food. See you around!

reviews.review_text: Delicious bowl and good portion. I enjoyed the cucumber salad and the fresh ingredients!

Delicious food, been eating here for more than 3 years and it s always tasty, fresh and clean. The portions are on the small side but very satisfying and good value for money since they maintained their standards over the years. I like their pilaf rice, root veggies, chicken, and vegan options. Would definitely recommend!
Highly recommend. One of us had the porketta bowl, the other a chicken bowl. Both were delicious, really well made and a decent size. Time and attention was clearly put into the preparation.

Couldnt gobble our food down fast enough! We ordered the Chicken Bowl and the Herbivore and were pleasantly surprised by the quality and flavour of both meals. Table service was polite, friendly, and prompt, and the restaurant is refreshingly clean with a good atmosphere for conversation to be had.
Delicious food, great service . I ll be back for the delicious food
Was walking on w 4th and googled  gluten free  - have a lot of dietary restrictions so was SO happy this place came up. I thoroughly enjoyed every single bite of the dish I got.
Delicious and healthy bowls and soups. Wish I found this place earlier, because it s difficult to find both healthy and delicious meals for a reasonable price at restaurants.
Everything was delicious! The regular bowl size was more than enough for one person.

I had the urge to write a review as I gobble up my Gobble for the nth time. It s my healthy, tasty, affordable comfort meal and I look forward to eating it every week. The sauces hit just right, the cranberry lentil salad is lightly sweet and refreshing, the chicken is cooked perfectly, and even the root veggies are so yummy. I love the nutritious variety we get in a bowl and I d shed a few tears if this restaurant ever closes.

This place is a hidden gem! Cute interior, the owner is the nicest guy. Freshly made, inspired, delicious food. Chose the feature Porchetta bowl, flavours and textures were perfectly balanced. Will definitely go back in a heartbeat. See you soon Gobble!

Love this place for a quick bite for wholesome healthy meal. Each of dishes on the menu are made with fresh ingredients and consistant with excellent selections for both vegetarians and meat eaters.  Friendly and helpful staff. Casual and cozy ambiance.  Very reasonable prices too.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the amazing feedback Pandora! We really do appreciate the positive reviews, it makes our day. Hope to see you soon!

reviews.review_text: Amazing places with amazing healthy bowls. So many protein options with extremely delicious home made sauces. Stop by here one day, you wont regret.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Glad you and your friend enjoyed everything Oleg! Thanks for spreading the word about us.

reviews.review_text: Best bowls! And good vibe. Healthy and delicious.

Delicious food, and not too expensive for this area. Definitely worth going to again. The only odd thing about the restaurant is that their card machine doesn t work very well - both me and the person behind me had to try two different cards to pay
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the review, hopefully its all fixed now.

reviews.review_text: This place is a gem. Honest, fresh food prepared with skill and care. I get cravings for their chickpea dish all the time. I dont even like chickpeas outside of this place. Thats some sort of food witchcraft that borders on miraculous.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Haha thanks for the great compliment Kevin! We have strict guidelines on how to appease the chickpea overlords. See you next time!

reviews.review_text: Food is always delicious and well done. =) I go there regularly for lunch

cosy little spot on one of Kitsilanos main streets. their friendly service make sure everyone is treated right and enjoying their dining experience. Great taste in music. highly recommend the butternut squash soup
So delicious and super healthy! Build your own bowl of proteins, veggies and carbs. So many vegan/vegetarian options
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the review Romy! See you next time!

reviews.review_text: Great option to pick up a healthy and delicious lunch! Blown away by how good my porketta bowl was - especially the lentils. No sacrificing on flavour here. I had been meaning to try this place for ages and Im so sad I didnt check it out sooner. Totally exceeded my expectations.
Great place for lunch! Delicious and healthy dishes and the steak was perfectly cooked.
Delicious food! This is a go-to for me. Its always yummy.

Love love love. I always get the crispy tofu bowl with rice pilaf, salad, and the lemon garlic Toume sauce. Gobble has unique and delicious flavour combinations and its nice to try if youre getting bored of your usual lunch! Also, its my favourite thing to order for takeaway right now, Ive had it 3 times this week

Im a regular customer here and love the quality and taste of the food. This is food made with love and skill and you can definitely taste it. My favourite dishes are the porchetta and chicken bowl, both of which have tender and juicy meats. Love that you can customize your bowls too.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you Clara! We appreciate your review, it means a lot to our team. See you soon!

reviews.review_text: Wow. I got the herbivore bowl expecting just a decent typical healthy lunch. It was extremely delicious- the regular size was filling enough but I could have kept eating.  Great place for celiac friendly food!

I have had Gobble twice and its amazing, I love their food! I had the bowl with steak, salad and lentils with Salsa Verde. Everything is cooked and prepared perfectly. The employee was really friendly and accommodating. I am craving this again now. I wish they were in East Van!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Awesome to hear you are satisfied with everything Flora,  until next time!

reviews.review_text: The food is exquisite! Again and again, my husband have dinners that are both delicious, and exactly what we want with no pretense! The staff, are great, the atmosphere is also great, just a warning to people who are allergic to pomegranate, tell them if u order the salad! Over all I highly recommend this place! Its Vegan Friendly, and Gluten and Dairy Free!
I really liked my meal here. I had a small lunch and really needed something to top it off. I had a regular size bowl. If I hadnt had lunch at all I would have gotten a full one.

I love the steak, roots, and rice pilaf! Havent tried their vegan main yet but it looks pretty good. Large portion is pretty hefty, so stick with regular unless you really want a lot of food (or leftovers). Their Smoked Honey Mustard is to die for, wish they would bottle that up!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks Eliot - well keep your suggestion in mind. Come by again soon!

reviews.review_text: Finally made it out after months of meaning to go. The only regret is not going sooner. The meat was absolutely delicious. Between two people we ordered the Pork and Steak options, both of which had a great texture and were very flavourful. We tried 3 of the 4 side options, which were all delicious and unique. Will definitely be back.

I m a regular customer here and I just keep wanting to come back for more. My favorite here is the porchetta bowl which always comes out fast and delicious. Usually, the porchetta would come with the skin but here it just tenders and juicy pork, very unique which I like. I would hope for more drinking options like a latte or a cappuccino but other than that this place never let me down!!

The portions for their food is perfect and all of the customization options for the bowls have been delicious. I have only tried the tofu bowl and it has arrived crispy every single time (which is not the case for many restaurants). My partner who has tried a variety of the meats has also always been extremely happy with the quality. Wed both recommend the Pilaf, Roots, or Winter Squash Chili as our favourite customization options. Ive ordered three times from Gobble now through different delivery services (Uber Eats, SkipTheDishes). The packaging for the food is nice and sturdy so everything has always arrived warm and intact. The first time I ordered from the delivery service, there were some issues with them finding a driver and Gobble had actually called to inform me of the delay so I wasnt left in the dark, and had remade the food so that it would arrive warm even though it wasnt their fault. This hasnt happened with any other restaurants Ive ordered from before and Im really impressed with their customer service.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Natasha. Thank you so much for your complimentary review! We are happy that you are enjoying our food, and that its arriving at your home warm and inviting :) Our customers are everything to us so thank you for letting us know how were doing. We will look forward to your next delivery order but hope that youll come visit us in-store sometime!

reviews.review_text: Delicious! Had the steak bowl with lentils and winter spicy squash. My group also tried the porchetta, with pilaf rice and salad, and the fried tofu. All very happy with the quality of the food. Portions were adequate.
Great local restaurant thats totally gluten free and dairy free. I love their keto and vegan bowls. Dietary restrictions: Gluten free and dairy free

Excellent and healthy food at a reasonable price, very authentic and friendly staff, and great atmosphere! Great for vegetarians/vegans as well as for meat lovers. I was really impressed by how good everything was; the meat was also extremely well cooked - and I am French so I do not give compliments easily ;) Really a great place to go to in Kitsilano
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for such a kind review Camille. Glad you and your friends enjoyed everything!

reviews.review_text: We did a group order through food.ee and oh my goodness, Gobble did not disappoint. There were a couple of us that ordered and we each got individually packaged meals. I ordered the large porchetta with winter squash and roots as my base, and honey mustard sauce. The root vegetables still had a good crunch, and the combination of the flavours were amazing! The porchetta was topped with chicharon, and that just took it to the next level. This portion was huge! For me,  the large is good enough for two servings. Would definitely order this again, but next time I would probably ask for additional sprinkles of chicharon, and Ill ask for some hot sauce on the side if possible. (Just because I would prefer it spicy.) But still good as is!!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Anna thank you for taking the time to write this awesome review! Detailed feedback helps us improve and keeps us on our toes. Hope you will enjoy it just as much the next time!

reviews.review_text: Super yummy!! I get the chicken bowl and its always delicious. Ill need to try out other things but the chicken bowl is always good I never do!
I dont know why I was surprised, but the food was really good! Really well seasoned and tasty vegetarian meal. The regular size was just the right amount for me. Will definitely go again.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hey Erin, thanks for coming by! Glad to hear you really enjoyed the food. Cant wait to serve you again!

reviews.review_text: Great place! Had 30 mins for lunch so decided to grab something to go. Food was good. Could see that the woman who was working was passionate about what she was serving. Would recommend getting the larger size if you re really hungry. Would definitely go back!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Julian thanks for the wonderful review. We are grateful for all the awesome guests here!

reviews.review_text: I dont think Ive ever made a google review before, but I am now because this place is amazing! Spread the word so they remain on W4th! Friendly staff and delicious food. I got the turkey with salad and root vegetables. This taste even better than my grandmas turkey dinner!! Well done Gobble!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Tamara, thank you so much for your flattering review! Were so glad you came in to see us and try our food. We love our local customers - youre the reason were here! Thanks again and we hope to see you again soon.

reviews.review_text: Healthy, clean and tasty Perfect lunch for work days!

Wow, once you take the first gobble, your not going to stop gobbling until your food is done. Atleast that was my experience since I just had one of the best meals of my life. If I lived in Vancouver, I would be a regular. Do yourself a favor and give this place a visit.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks so much Sean, come back soon!

reviews.review_text: Fantastic little restaurant. I love the porchetta. Healthy choices with lots of gluten free options. The chicken soup is also so delicious! Highly recommended!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you Yvette! Happy to hear that you enjoyed everything. See you again soon!

reviews.review_text: Gobble was great! The bowls and soups are very tasty and prices very reasonable. Staff were nice too. Would recommend to anyone looking for a hearthy meal!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Awesome! Thanks for the feedback and see you soon!

reviews.review_text: High quality ingredients, allergen free and organic. Food was tasty. Great service too. Keep up the good work. Hope you can expand your ingredients.
We have lived a block away for 6 years and only discovered Gobble recently. GREAT place. The food is healthy and tastes amazing.  Reasonably priced too.
Love this place! The portions and quality are great, the food is refreshingly different. I always get the porchetta with half roots and half rice.
great quality healthy food great for lunch Food : 5/5
Came by during khatsalano days. And their pork burrito was gorgeous. The meat was sooooo good and the staff were super friendly! Ill be back for sure.
My fav. Often get Uber Eats delivered when Im busy and want something healthy. Im not vegetarian but the Crispy Tofu with Aioli is bomb
We had the steak/root veg/summer salad and tofu/lentil/rice. The taste was amazing.
Loved the food, super yummy and a nice place to sit.
This place is a hidden gem in Kitsilano and Ive always been baffled this place isnt packed everyday. The food is healthy, fresh and most importantly flavorful and delicious.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Happy to hear that, thank you!

reviews.review_text: Fresh and tasty food! p.s. a bit pricey for me, but it is in normal range! So if you want to eat healthy go there!
The breakfast here shattered my expectation insanely good and not expensive at all. This is my new favorite cafe in the area!
So so good. This place is a constant favourite!
Delicious food with a friendly and open atmosphere. I cant get enough of the smoked honey mustard sauce and the root veggies!
Great value here, delicious homestyle food, well seasoned meats/veg and generous portions. Repeat customer!
Simple, delicious, comfort food - a great addition to the neighbourhood. I ve been a few times and it does not disappoint.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks Masi for coming by! Looking forward to serving you again.

reviews.review_text: I don t live near by, but I come to kits just to eat here time to time. I love their steak and root veggies.
Cutest restaurant, I love their food and service is always the friendliest!
Fresh food, nice clean place.
The food here is fantastic. It is great grab and go and great for catering conferences and workshops.
Really deliciously filling and kind staff really well hand made dishes and treats fits a group of 19 all together
best meat in town. gormet quality food for reasonable price. huge portions
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks Peter! Come by again next time you are in the neighbourhood

reviews.review_text: Its nice to find a delicious, balanced meal in a restaurant. Everything was perfectly cooked and delicious.
Chickpea with smoked honey mustard sauce, salad and pumpkin curry lentils is sooo goood
Delicious!!!! I will come back here again!!
Amazing food and service. Another staple vegetarian joint near home.
Best Turkey Ive ever had and great service as well!
I love Gobble. It s my happy place and their food is soooo good
Everything was delicious, and the service was excellent.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you Anita, we are very glad to hear that. Hope to see you soon!

reviews.review_text: The herbivore bowl is amazing!
Best bowl in Kits.
Simply splendid
Healthy and satisfying
A great spot!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks Jerth see you soon!
